{"tid":1912612,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有人寫咗篇‘炒飯物理學’既論文，話日後可以做炒飯機械人","createTime":"2020-03-06T07:52:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-06T09:03:02.000Z","uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4f26ebd7c674321d73aaa9a6cbaa7402387b4f55","tid":1912612,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T07:52:11.000Z","msg":"The Physics of tossing fried rice<br />\n<a href=\"https://royalsocietypublishing.org/doi/10.1098/rsif.2019.0622\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Froyalsocietypublishing.org%2Fdoi%2F10.1098%2Frsif.2019.0622&d=%2FrzxgVsCSRBeEmt1flTkcNLD3cQOkzCKckuFp%2FmPVdU%3D&h=0823cea8\" target=\"_blank\">https://royalsocietypublishing.org/doi/10.1098/rsif.2019.0622</a><br />\n<br />\n林行止介紹<br />\n<br />\n事實上，經此論文深入精微的剖析，相信很快便有人發明一種模仿力極強的「人形機械人」（humanoid robat），以代替「炒飯（菜）師傅」的工作，那不僅令廚房機械化更進一步（波士頓的SPYCE餐廳已有機械人廚師），而且可把我國廚師的獨門工夫「炒功」（Stir-frying）向全球推廣；更重要的是，有機械人代勞，廚師因為長年累月「拋鑊」（〔甩鍋〕wok tossing）而令肩胛發炎腫痛的「職業病」便會消失。據作者們「明查」所得的數據，職業「拋鑊」廚師（候鑊）肩膀肌肉拉傷率高達百分之六十四點五；這些數字是他們實地「調查」五位分別在台灣和河南飯店服務的主廚（入廚年資都在二十年左右）的結果！<br />\n<a href=\"http://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2394765\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Flanding%2FmobArticle2%2Fid%2F2394765&d=%2FrzxgVsCSRBeEmt1flTkcNLD3cQOkzCKckuFp%2FmPVdU%3D&h=44bc3eb7\" target=\"_blank\">http://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2394765</a><br />\n<br />\n真係得？！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b69e59bca96d30067066098b517ff7409bec4a7b","tid":1912612,"uid":82912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4f26ebd7c674321d73aaa9a6cbaa7402387b4f55","tid":1912612,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T07:52:11.000Z","msg":"The Physics of tossing fried rice<br />\n<a href=\"https://royalsocietypublishing.org/doi/10.1098/rsif.20